 private, I would love if you could help me with my big novel that I'm writing, I like the way you write, it's so fascinating, I want to learn to write as you do... Please contact me at my email: cosmin08dumea@gmail.com <br />I hope in a your answer, thanks! <br />                                   -  Cosmin Dumea ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 month ago","ctime":"March 26 2017, 16:41:54 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Hi Mr Martin :) ","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://cosmin08.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"cosmin08","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"cosmin08","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://cosmin08.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"cosmin08","ctime_ts":1490546514,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?replyto=25905488","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25905488#t25905488","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25905488#t25905488","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25905488#t25905488","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"grrm","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25905488,"talkid":101193,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25905488#t25905488","above":25904720,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"I'm sorry, but I am too busy with my own work to be able to help anyone else with theirs.<br /><br />There are some excellent workshops and courses out there, however.<br /><br />And you might want to take a look at the FAQ on my website.<br /><br />Good luck.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 month ago","ctime":"March 26 2017, 20:22:20 UTC","parent":25904720,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: Hi Mr Martin :) ","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1490559740,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/125911873/77518781","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?replyto=25907024","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25907024#t25907024","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25907024#t25907024","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25907024#t25907024","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"valcarenghi","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://valcarenghi.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25907024,"talkid":101199,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25907024#t25907024","upictitle":"valcarenghi: pic#125911873","article":"Wow, I wish I could be there for the April 2 event. N Scott Momaday is one of my favourite living authors and a wonderfully eloquent (not to mention sonorous!) speaker.<br /><br />You always host the coolest events at the Jean Cocteau. A pity I live on the other side of the continent!","si