 me he loves how much you help other authors and that you've asked him to stop by before but his schedule just didn't work out that time. He also said he definitely wants to stop by on one tour or another. . . Basically, I just want to ask you to continue pestering him to stop by for an author event someday. He's one of my favorite modern fantasy authors.   ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 month ago","ctime":"March 30 2017, 20:07:51 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Love your author events","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/UTLonghorn1","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Sean Hall","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1785679","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=63422077&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Sean Hall","ctime_ts":1490904471,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?replyto=25912912","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25912912#t25912912","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25912912#t25912912","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25912912#t25912912","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"grrm","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25912912,"talkid":101222,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/528720.html?thread=25912912#t25912912","above":25912400,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"With all the authors on hand for GUNS,